OL,3,CPlans announced to overhaul how water
OL,4,Cis managed in Wales
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has announced
OL,7,Fplans to overhaul how water is
OL,8,Fmanaged, regulated, and delivered in
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FIt follows concerns over rising water
OL,12,Fbills, pollution, and a system many
OL,13,Ffeel is no longer fit for purpose.
OL,15,FDeputy First Minister Huw Irranca-
OL,16,FDavies outlined the proposals in the
OL,17,FSenedd today, following the release of
OL,18,Fthe Independent Water Commission's
OL,19,Freport.
