OL,3,CPlans announced to overhaul how water
OL,4,Cis managed in Wales
OL,6,F"That has to change."
OL,8,FOne proposal is the creation of a new,
OL,9,Fdedicated economic regulator for water
OL,10,Fin Wales, which would incorporate
OL,11,Fplanning responsibilities.
OL,13,FAccording to the plans, this would
OL,14,Fallow for a more integrated approach
OL,15,Fto water management, distinct from the
OL,16,Fexisting UK-wide oversight structures.
