OL,3,CPlans announced to overhaul how water
OL,4,Cis managed in Wales
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has said it will
OL,7,Fconsult the public on the new model
OL,8,Fbefore the end of the year, promising
OL,9,Fthat any reforms will reflect "Welsh
OL,10,Fpriorities."
OL,12,FBut questions remain whether a new
OL,13,Fregulatory body will be genuinely
OL,14,Findependent or simply shift
OL,15,Fresponsibilities without addressing
OL,16,Fdeeper structural issues.
OL,18,FThe announcement also included a
OL,19,Fcommitment to seek new legislative
OL,20,Fpowers for the Senedd.
