OL,3,CPlans announced to overhaul how water
OL,4,Cis managed in Wales
OL,6,FIf granted, these would give Wales
OL,7,Ffull control over its water industry
OL,8,Ffor the first time- a move that would
OL,9,Frequire agreement from Westminster.
OL,11,FWhile the proposals have been pitched
OL,12,Fas a move away from the privatised,
OL,13,Fcompetition-led model inherited pre-
OL,14,Fdevolution, the full details of what a
OL,15,Fnew "ethical and collaborative" system
OL,16,Fwould look like remain to be seen.
