OL,3,CPlans announced to overhaul how water
OL,4,Cis managed in Wales
OL,6,FA transition plan is expected to be co-
OL,7,Fdeveloped with the UK Government and
OL,8,Fother stakeholders to avoid
OL,9,Finstability. Interim measures, such as
OL,10,Fupdated strategic policy guidance to
OL,11,Fregulators like Ofwat, will be put in
OL,12,Fplace while the changes are developed.
OL,14,FThe Deputy First Minister acknowledged
OL,15,Fthe scale of the challenge: "Reforming
OL,16,Fthe water sector is a complex, long-
OL,17,Fterm task ` but it's also an
OL,18,Fopportunity to create a better water
OL,19,Fsystem and show what devolution can
OL,20,Fachieve.
