OL,3,CPlans announced to overhaul how water
OL,4,Cis managed in Wales
OL,6,F"By working together ` with the UK
OL,7,FGovernment, with regulators and water
OL,8,Fcompanies, and with communities across
OL,9,FWales ` we can build a system that
OL,10,Fdelivers for our environment, our
OL,11,Feconomy and our people for decades to
OL,12,Fcome."
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government will publish a
OL,15,Fdetailed "vision" document later this
OL,16,Fyear, setting out next steps and
OL,17,Finviting input from communities,
OL,18,Fbusinesses, and regulators.
